column5: We waste too much energy following this tabloid drivel and the pop stars they focus on.
x2. My thoughts are "who cares what a pop star does". Stupider and less good looking people have does stupider things.
Another example of British ex-pats trying to ruin great Canadian resources! Jim
Dual nationality actually, but if Beiber is the standard to which Canadians aspire to...yup...lol...Brit and proud.
Like an "Ass", right? Sure honing his skills into becoming a great one at that.
